{"tid":1415260,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"機場要人！東涌青衣撚入部同我入機場！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T15:12:45.000Z","uid":104470,"like":121,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"af98f11e4299109302702e1e99a01201186735b4","tid":1415260,"uid":104470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:03.000Z","msg":"全部唔知做乜野企晒係地鐵站門口<br />\nOn99企係度捉精靈啊依家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係識得屌人影相 嚇走晒啲街坊<br />\n口號又唔會嗌<br />\n標語又冇<br />\n而且東涌依家冇狗<br />\n唔知守係度有咩意義<br />\n<br />\n作為東涌人 青衣人<br />\n不如把地理優勢入機場支援下機場既手足好過啦<br />\n講左幾多百萬次機場最有戰略意義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n淨係依家係地鐵站出面既人入機場<br />\n已經多好多人幫手<br />\n<br />\n[機場防線] 再咁落去我地無可能贏<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1414005\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1414005</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ffe64894ef0e5cade98efb949fb527924b3ba5fe","tid":1415260,"uid":104470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:27.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c0730885df74c48024f8b4d08915a5988f331756","tid":1415260,"uid":104470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f2e696ce6f12ba29ed47c618017dabb0dc37a63","tid":1415260,"uid":104470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T13:27:51.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces